item.title: Jan 20th, 2024
item.description: This is my first page - it will likely be modified many times. Currently testing the date property as well as the category property. Things to note when working on this site: Logseq-schrodinger uses YAML for the Hugo front-matter. It will convert Logseq page-properties to Hugo front matter. Logseq keywords are lowercase converted to Hugo keywords, and category in Logseq is translated to categories for use with Hugo. Logseq links (like_this) are stripped of and .
